English:
Urged on by the voice, I took a leap of faith.
But what the heck happened?
Chinese:
在那個“聲音”的催促下，我忍不住「跳了進來」……
到底發生了什麼事？
Korean:
"목소리"에 이끌리는 대로,「뛰어들어」버렸어…
대체 무슨 일이 일어난 거지?
German:
Nachdem die Stimme mich ermutigt hat, habe ich
mich getraut. Aber was ist geschehen?

English: It looks like I can go forward after all.
